quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  40,26,"“Ndipo Farawo adati: “Ndilekeni ndimuphe Mûsa; ampemphe Mbuye wakeyo (kuti ampulumutse kwa ine). Ine ndikuopera kuti angasinthe chipembedzo chanu, kapena kufalitsa chisokonezo pa dziko.”"
  40,27,"“Ndipo Mûsa adati (kwa Farawo pa modzi ndi anthu ake): “Ine ndadzitchinjiriza ndi Mbuye wanga amenenso ali Mbuye wanu (ku chiwembu) chochokera kwa aliyense wodzikweza, wosakhulupirira za tsiku la chiwerengero"
  40,28,"“Ndipo munthu wokhulupirira, wochokera kubanja la Farawo yemwe adali kubisa chikhulupiliro chake, adawalankhula (anthu ake): “Kodi muphe munthu chifukwa chakuti iye akunena kuti: ‘Mbuye wanga ndi Allah,’ chikhalirecho wakubweretserani zisonyezo zoonekera poyera, zochokera kwa Mbuye wanu? Ndipo ngati ali wabodza pa zomwe akunena ndiye kuti kuipa kwa bodzalo kum’bwerera yekha. Koma ngati ali woona (pazomwe akukulonjezani), ndiye kuti gawo lina la zomwe (chilango) akukulonjezani likupezani; ndithu Allah saongola munthu wopyola malire, wabodza la mkunkhuniza!”"
  40,29,"““E inu anthu anga! Ufumu walero ngwanu: mwagonjetsa dziko (la Iguputo). Ndani amene angatipulumutse ku chilango cha Allah ngati chitatidzera?” Farawo adati: “Sindikukupatsani maganizo koma okhawo ndikuwaona (kuti ndi abwino) ndiponso sindikukuwongolerani koma kunjira yoongoka.”"
  40,30,"“Ndipo munthu wokhulupirira uja adanena: “E inu anthu anga! Ine ndikukuoperani (za tsiku la masautso) monga tsiku la magulu (omwe adaukira aneneri awo).”"
  40,31,"““Monga chikhalidwe cha anthu a Nuh, Âdi, Samudi ndi anthu omwe adadza pambuyo pawo. Koma Allah safuna kupondereza akapolo Ake.”"
  40,32,““Ndiponso anthu anga! Ine ndikukuoperani tsiku la kuitanizana (anthu).”
  40,33,"““Tsiku limene mudzathawa ndi kutembenuza misana yanu; pomwe simudzakhala ndi mtetezi ku chilango cha Allah; ndipo amene Allah wamulekelera kusokera (chifukwa cha zochita zake zoipa), ndiye kuti sangapeze muongoli.”"